=== Description

A attempt to let users enter nodes in Max De Marzi's Neovigator:
	- from branch jundalisay
	- using erb instead of haml
	- using sqlite, activerecord and postgres as a secondary or temp db

=== How To

  bundle install
  rake neo4j:install
  rake neo4j:start
  rackup
  
Go to http://localhost:9292 to see it running.  

Enter a node id in the search box and click "Load"

See an example running on heroku at {http://neovigator.herokuapp.com}[http://neovigator.herokuapp.com]

